[FILE:485:descriptions/desc.single]
graphlayouts: Additional Layout Algorithms for Network Visualizations

Several new layout algorithms to visualize networks are provided which are
not part of 'igraph'. Most are based on the concept of stress majorization
by Gansner et al. (2004) &lt;<a
href="https://doi.org/10.1007%2F978-3-540-31843-9_25"
target="_top">doi:10.1007/978-3-540-31843-9_25</a>&gt;. Some more specific
algorithms allow the user to emphasize hidden group structures in networks
or focus on specific nodes.


